'''Dagmawi Yimer''' (yavutse 6 Ukuboza 1977), ni umukinnyi wa filimi uvuka muri etiyopiya ariko atuye mu [[Butaliyani]]. <ref name="filme">http://www.filme-aus-afrika.de/EN/film-database/persons/personen-details/w/3509/</ref> <ref name="themigrationist">https://themigrationist.net/2014/11/05/journeying-into-the-hidden-world-of-migrants-with-filmmaker-dagmawi-yimer/</ref> Niwe kandi washinze hamwe na visi perezida wa Archivio delle Memorie Migranti. <ref name="parse">https://parsejournal.com/authors/dagmawi-yimer/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 6 Ukuboza 1977 mu mujyi muto wa Kirkos, [[Addis Ababa|Addis Abeba]], muri Etiyopiya. Mbere yo kuva mu gihugu, yize amategeko i Addis Abeba mu 2003. <ref name="yimer">https://iffr.com/en/persons/dagmawi-yimer</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2005, yavuye muri Etipoya kubera imvururu zikomeye nyuma ya politiki. Yavuye mu rugo atabimenyesheje se ariko nyina na mushiki we gusa. Yambutse ubutayu hagati ya Sudani na Libiya nyuma yambuka inyanja ya Mediterane mu mpera za Nyakanga 2006. Amaherezo yageze mu Butaliyani nyuma y'urugendo ruteye akaga. <ref name="yimer" /> Yimukiye i Lampedusa ahatura kuva ku ya 30 Nyakanga 2006. Muri Gicurasi 2007, yitabiriye amasomo yo kuvuga amashusho yishyirahamwe rya Asinitas. Muri kiriya gihe, yakoze documentaire ye ya mbere ''Ubutayu ninyanja'' afatanyije na Asinitas, Zalab na Aamod. 

Hagati aho, yimukiye mu bunzi bw’indimi n’umuco mu ishyirahamwe rya Asinitas Onlus, mu ishuri rimwe ry’abataliyani ry’abasaba ubuhunzi, impunzi n’abimukira. Mu myaka ye myiza kuva 2007 kugeza 2008, Yimer yakoze firime ngufi zizwi cyane: ''Lo scabocchio'', ''Le sagome'', na ''Caravan'' .  Noneho yakoze ''Welcome to your home'' hamwe na Marco Carsetti. Noneho yari umwe mu banditsi ba documentaire ya biografiya ''Ngwino un uomo sulla terra'' yibanze ku kwimuka uva muri Libiya ujya i Burayi.  Filime yakozwe na Asinitas Onlus, kubufatanye bwa Zalab. Muri 2009, Yimer yakiriye Umwihariko muri BIF & ST kuri documentaire. 

Muri 2011, yakoze firime ''Solo il mare'', yibanda ku kirwa cya Lampedusa. Noneho muri 2013, Yimer yakoze ''Va 'Pensiero'' ashingiye ku nkuru yambukiranya ibitero bibiri by'ivanguramoko muri Milan na Florence. Muri 2015, yakoze firime ebyiri: ''Asmat-Amazina'' na ''Benvenuti mu Butaliyani'' . 

